Replace the inline kill-job logic in `retryOrFailureResponse` with a call to the new `broadcastKill` method to reuse the extracted logic. Add the new public static `broadcastKill` method after the `NodeOperationRunnable` inner class to centralize the node-excluding kill request dispatching with logging.

